text.tspan: Annual change in population aged 5 to 9 years, 1951 to 2100
Population yearly increment, estimated as the difference between the population on 1st of July of the year
indicated and the population a year before. This only includes individuals aged 5-9. Projections from 2024
onwards are based on the UN's medium scenario.
Data source: UN, World Population Prospects (2024)
